substep.action:
Capture from caller inputs and `thoughts metadata`:
- {{bundle_dir}}, {{ticket_slug}}, {{ticket_alias}}
- {{branch}}, {{target_branch}}, {{worktree_path}}
- {{owner}}/{{repo}} (from `gh repo view --json owner,name`)
- {{verification_doc_path}} = {bundle_dir}/verification-YYYY-MM-DD-{ticket_slug}.md
